            FirstName = <>h__TransparentIdentifier0.s.FirstName,

2024-04-19 12:17:00.182 +03:00 [DBG] Generated query execution expression: 
'queryContext => new SingleQueryingEnumerable<DalBookDetailsDto>(
    (RelationalQueryContext)queryContext, 
    RelationalCommandCache.QueryExpression(
        Projection Mapping:
            FirstName -> 0
            LastName -> 1
            Title -> 2
            CheckStartDate -> 3
            CheckEndDate -> 4
        SELECT s0.FirstName, s0.LastName, b.Title, s.CheckStartDate, s.CheckEndDate
        FROM StudentBook AS s
